          <p><strong>Colors:</strong> Ultra Violet &amp; Pale Silver</p>
          <p><strong>Animal:</strong> Snowy Owl</p>
          <p><strong>Plant:</strong> Mandrake</p>
          <p><strong>Personality:</strong> They move through the veil of reality with ease, ever curious and enigmatic, guiding others to hidden truths with both clarity and mischief.</p>
          <p><strong>Parents:</strong> <a href="#Astraea" class="relation-link">Astraea</a> and <a href="#Umbrya" class="relation-link">Umbrya</a></p>
          <p><strong>Spouse:</strong> <a href="#Silvaris" class="relation-link">Silvaris</a></p>
          <p><strong>Siblings:</strong> <a href="#Serendya" class="relation-link">Serendya</a>, <a href="#Zephyros" class="relation-link">Zephyros</a>, and <a href="#Faelys" class="relation-link">Faelys</a></p>
          <p><strong>Children:</strong> <a href="#Nythalos" class="relation-link">Nythalos</a> and <a href="#Somnorys" class="relation-link">Somnorys</a> </p>
