        <p><strong>Animal:</strong> Black Scorpion</p>
        <p><strong>Plant:</strong> Corpse Flower</p>
        <p><strong>Personality:</strong> Terroryx rarely speaks, for their presence alone is communication enough. They embody the paralyzing dread that freezes minds and the frantic terror that drives bodies to flee. In their eyes, fear is neither good nor evil—merely a primal force of survival and control.</p>
        <p><strong>Parents:</strong> <a href="#Volthar" class="relation-link">Volthar</a> and <a href="#Soltheron" class="relation-link">Soltheron</a></p>
