          <h3>Vindictrix</h3>
          <p><strong>Domain:</strong> Retribution, Vengeance &amp; Cosmic Balance</p>
          <p><strong>Pronouns:</strong> She/Her</p>
          <p><strong>Symbol:</strong> Balanced scales with sword</p>
          <p><strong>Colors:</strong> Vermilion &amp; Gunmetal Gray</p>
          <p><strong>Animal:</strong> Eagle Owl</p>
          <p><strong>Plant:</strong> Thistle</p>
          <p><strong>Personality:</strong> Vindictrix arrives when justice alone is not enough. She is the consequence that follows hubris, the reckoning that follows cruelty. Her vengeance is not cruel but precisely measured—always proportional, never excessive.</p>
          <p><strong>Parents:</strong> <a href="#Corvanyx" class="relation-link">Corvanyx</a> and <a href="#Erythros" class="relation-link">Erythros</a></p>
