         <p><strong>Plant:</strong> Passionflower</p>
         <p><strong>Personality:</strong> Animira speaks in whispers heard only by one's innermost self. She represents the part of each being that remains unchanged through all transformations—witnessing, experiencing, yet never fully seen.</p>
         <p><strong>Parents:</strong> <a href="#Rithmosa" class="relation-link">Rithmosa</a> and <a href="#Somnorys" class="relation-link">Somnorys</a></p>
